    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，Direct Line 拒绝 Ageas 31 亿英镑的收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/uk-insurer-direct-line-said-to-reject-ageas-takeover-approach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ageas表示，正在考虑对Direct Line Insurance Group Plc提出可能的收购要约，并概述了对这家英国保险公司的收购要约，收购价将较周二收盘价溢价42.8%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/uk-insurer-direct-line-said-to-reject-ageas-takeover-approach</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:45:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>资本市场超出预期，加拿大皇家银行超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/rbc-tops-estimates-as-capital-markets-outperform-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行超出了分析师的预期，因为该公司资本市场和财富管理业务的表现强于预期，抵消了贷款损失准备金的增加和费用的增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/rbc-tops-estimates-as-capital-markets-outperform-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>每年都有收益的对冲基金看到不良债务反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/hedge-fund-that-gains-every-year-sees-2024-distressed-debt-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家对冲基金自 2015 年成立以来每年都取得收益，去年的回报率达到创纪录的 16%，该基金押注于陷入困境的新兴市场主权国家的反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/hedge-fund-that-gains-every-year-sees-2024-distressed-debt-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:52:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
